通個生產成本、研發成本<br />\n亞洲整體人工低、福利差、工時較長，所以拉低左台積電、三叔個生產成本、研發成本<br />\n<br />\n美國公司係美國投資1000萬美金，最後只請到一隊工程師2年<br />\n亞洲公司係亞洲投資1000萬美金，最後請到3隊工程師2年<br />\n久而久知，慢慢亞洲廠就開始贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n晶圓生產遲d就好似白色家電、汽車零件咁轉哂落去東亞生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b4bd092615f3f5f0fff27cc5f26f0bcd49188f","tid":1828891,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:36:24.000Z","msg":"14nm++++++++++<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344efa4c4079e9db0eb2c8829c51a8e292cc1c8a","tid":1828891,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aa691eabaf552d5a793364273e8fcd19e971a5","tid":1828891,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"煙條殞落"}]}